.DT
create_auto_load_file
Disk World creator help
create_auto_load_file

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
create_auto_load_file -  This method creates a save file for the specified objects autoloading capability.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int create_auto_load_file(mixed ob,
int fixed_num)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^ob%^RESET%^ - the object to get an autoload number for
%^BOLD%^fixed_num%^RESET%^ - the file number to write to
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the auto load number.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/shops/inherit/player_craft_shop_base.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method creates a save file for the specified objects autoloading
capability.  If the number to write to is non-null then it will
write to that object.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
save_it()

.EP

